{"tid":2297992,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無試過 發夢 夢見EX ??","createTime":"2020-11-23T17:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T05:21:10.000Z","uid":31238,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b687e5b8eba49a086e3f005aef10ed22d028efce","tid":2297992,"uid":31238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"巴打們有無試過 發夢 夢到個EX？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同EX分開咗差唔多2年了<br />\n琴日我係夢入面見到佢，<br />\n夢入面我同佢應該係處於熱戀時期<br />\n大家都怕怕羞羞咁，然後拖住對方<br />\n但係好快咁 我就意識到自己係夢入面，<br />\n可能因為我清楚知道呢個畫面根本唔係真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而當我開始意識到我係夢入面時<br />\n我無令自己即刻醒，反而係選擇繼續停留夢入面 (唔知大家明唔明個種感覺, 當知道自己係夢入面時, 盡力嘗試再停留係夢入面)<br />\n<br />\n但結果，我係唔成功嘅，我終於都係醒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我醒咗之後，無空虛 無失落<br />\n反而係會心微笑，因為真係好甜嘅一個夢<br />\n<br />\n因為我真係好耐好耐...<br />\n都無咁真實 咁近距離見過你笑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實同你都分開咗咁耐了，其實也好奇 想知你過得還好嗎？<br />\n唉，點解你既影子總係隔一排就 浮現我腦海入面<br />\n<br />\n有時經過以前一齊手牽手 笑住行過既路<br />\n經過以前一齊食過既餐廳， 當時話之後想再食 但再沒有之後<br />\n經過以前一齊食過 但發現已經結業既餐廳<br />\n心入面 總會有種景物依舊，人事全非；<br />\n甚至景物全非，人事全非<br />\n<br />\n通常我不會經常想起你，<br />\n只是有時不經意想起你的話，都總是比較深<br />\n<br />\n純綷叫下春<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86633bfc8184c23339488e090158ac3aa7d02400","tid":2297992,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦屌你老母扮感性"},{"pid":"bce6d164aae818854ae26ceee4dd11e811b76ec6","tid":2297992,"uid":31238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86633bfc8184c23339488e090158ac3aa7d02400","tid":2297992,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"收撚皮啦屌你老母扮感性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"好波 巴打，屌得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2433b2f7c005d836fc9c6707585075f7c6b73dfb","tid":2297992,"uid":244889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T03:25:49.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔知點解<br />\n明明分咗兩年<br />\n兩年間完全無諗起佢<br />\n突然有日夢到<br />\n攪到依家對以前hurt佢既事好有罪惡感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4de54a99d2810c94ddb2dd6bacbcdcc3a3ad94","tid":2297992,"uid":11365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T03:28:02.000Z","msg":"情聖上身咩戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6453321fbbdf449fcad9365643db07e530fd66df","tid":2297992,"uid":196459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"係咁美好當初就唔會分開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3132e3a5672a9f900c15c0b6cef46ada103e6c","tid":2297992,"uid":236505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6453321fbbdf449fcad9365643db07e530fd66df","tid":2297992,"uid":196459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"係咁美好當初就唔會分開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"就算係分開 <br />\n都會有美好既一刻架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fa73957b0446a0c1ab4092e4d1ccb4eabbc23a","tid":2297992,"uid":119446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"前日又夢見你<br />\n我地又去左日本玩<br />\n就好似以前咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d84725a34333a814a0151431354dd382ce9d50","tid":2297992,"uid":375148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:03:58.000Z","msg":"同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf3fddb04c70d227e3f37e68cadc8c3704133a0","tid":2297992,"uid":220772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:05:27.000Z","msg":"醒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42387ea4cfd92b0977bb33b63c0158f8ba393360","tid":2297992,"uid":350206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:21:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>選擇繼續停留夢入面 (唔知大家明唔明個種感覺, 當知道自己係夢入面時, 盡力嘗試再停留係夢入面)<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n我都會咁樣做 唔起身繼續同佢一齊"}]}